list.label: Hostname
list.name: hostname
list.query: show tag values from "intel.procfs.cpu.user_percentage" with key = hostname

list.label: Disk
list.name: disk
list.query: show tag values from "intel.procfs.disk.merged_read" with key = disk where hostname = '$hostname'

list.label: Interface
list.name: iface
list.query: show tag values from "intel.procfs.iface.bytes_recv" with key = interface where hostname = '$hostname'

list.label: Filesystem
list.name: fs
list.query: show tag values from "intel.procfs.filesystem.inodes_free" with key = filesystem where hostname = '$hostname'

list.label: S.M.A.R.T.
list.name: smart
list.query: show tag values from "intel.disk.smart.casetemperature" with key = device where hostname = '$hostname'
